{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-js","path":"/post/100-days-of-gatsby","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"0e24fa25-5bde-598a-97fa-e70a1dc285f3","frontmatter":{"title":"#100DaysOfGatsby Challenge","hero":{"id":"d041cfdd-b3eb-57ee-a6f3-b523701c4584","childImageSharp":{"id":"9dbdd013-944f-503e-933b-9565c4810641","fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.9047619047619047,"src":"/static/952cdbf6c0216236449e61298b0ebdb7/5134e/100daysofgatsby.png","srcSet":"/static/952cdbf6c0216236449e61298b0ebdb7/69585/100daysofgatsby.png 200w,\n/static/952cdbf6c0216236449e61298b0ebdb7/497c6/100daysofgatsby.png 400w,\n/static/952cdbf6c0216236449e61298b0ebdb7/5134e/100daysofgatsby.png 786w","sizes":"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px"}}},"date":"2020-03-16","path":"post/100-days-of-gatsby","tags":["learning-to-code","gatsby"]},"html":"<p>After months of learning, I finally decided to use <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/\">Gatsby</a> to make my website instead of <a href=\"https://nuxtjs.org/\">NuxtJS</a>. For now, I like <a href=\"https://reactjs.org/\">React</a> more than <a href=\"https://vuejs.org/\">Vue</a>. I think maybe because I'm such a beginner of modern web development and React's docs are more friendly for beginner than Vue's (on my perspective).</p>\n<p>And Gatsby is a powerful framework for React. I'm using it to make a film review website for my own brand '添糖电影院' on WeChat for weeks. The more I learn, the much I like it.</p>\n<p>To improve the understanding of Gatsby, I'd love to join the <a href=\"https://www.gatsbyjs.org/blog/100days\">#100DaysOfGatsby coding challenge</a>. And today is the results for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><strong>Challenge 1</strong>: Greate a Gatsby blog from scratch. I'm using the <a href=\"https://getuikit.com\">UIkit</a> for CSS.</li>\n<li><strong>Challenge 2</strong>: Host my Gatsby site for free.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>I'll use this blog to track my coding progress.</p>"},"site":{"id":"Site","siteMetadata":{"title":"CY Is Here"}}},"pageContext":{"pathName":"post/100-days-of-gatsby","prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"post/2020-03-17-gatsby-image","tags":["learning-to-code","gatsby"],"title":"Auto-Optimize Images On MY Gatsby Site"}},"next":{"frontmatter":{"path":"post/2020-oscar-contending-screenplays","tags":["电影","剧本"],"title":"【转】2020年奥斯卡剧本"}}}}}